CHECK IN:
- Render the dates available
- On click, go to the CHECKOUT CALENDAR
  -In the CHECKIN CALENDAR:
    -All of the available dates are still clickable
  -In the CHECKOUT CALENDAR:
    -Cannot change the checkin date
    -Cross out the dates that behind the stay date
    -Cross out the dates that are below the minimum stay
      -Cannot click the dates that are below the minimum stay
    -The range of dates that are still clickable are clickable
    -EXTRA: highlight the dates that are recommended (minimum stay)
  

